OSC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lille_OSC\"}, {\"begin\": 272, \"end\": 277, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lille_OSC\", \"score\": 0.9997363056088212, \"rank\": 0.0002636700961436064, \"text\": \"Lille\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lille_OSC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lille_OSC\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"NOAH EAGLE\", \"from\": 174, \"to\": 184}, {\"ngram\": \"a blast\", \"from\": 212, \"to\": 219}, {\"ngram\": \"week\", \"from\": 227, \"to\": 231}, {\"ngram\": \"the hospitality\", \"from\": 282, \"to\": 297}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 343, \"to\": 352}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We had a great time and the crowds were off the charts from day one all the way through.\", \"from\": 354, \"to\": 442, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a great time\", \"from\": 361, \"to\": 373}, {\"ngram\": \"the crowds\", \"from\": 378, \"to\": 388}, {\"ngram\": \"the charts\", \"from\": 398, \"to\": 408}, {\"ngram\": \"day\", \"from\": 414, \"to\": 417}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But very excited to be back in Paris.\", \"from\": 444, \"to\": 481, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 475, \"end\": 480, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999875456574261, \"rank\": 1.2454497644334101e-05, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And I think the arena will be bursting with a lot of energy on both the men's and women's side.\", \"from\": 482, \"to\": 577, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the arena\", \"from\": 494, \"to\": 503}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 526, \"to\": 531}, {\"ngram\": \"energy\", \"from\": 535, \"to\": 541}, {\"ngram\": \"both the men's and women's side\", \"from\": 545, \"to\": 576}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We have great teams that made it through from the quarterfinals all the way on.\", \"from\": 578, \"to\": 657, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"great teams\", \"from\": 586, \"to\": 597}, {\"ngram\": \"the quarterfinals\", \"from\": 624, \"to\": 641}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The United States the headliner for both, claiming the number one seeds for both sides.\", \"from\": 658, \"to\": 745, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 662, \"end\": 675, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9938705740866977, \"rank\": 0.005104225290442661, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the headliner\", \"from\": 676, \"to\": 689}, {\"ngram\": \"the number one seeds\", \"from\": 709, \"to\": 729}, {\"ngram\": \"both sides\", \"from\": 734, \"to\": 744}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The men have looked incredibly strong and the women have dominated the competition.\", \"from\": 746, \"to\": 829, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The men\", \"from\": 746, \"to\": 753}, {\"ngram\": \"the women\", \"from\": 788, \"to\": 797}, {\"ngram\": \"the competition\", \"from\": 813, \"to\": 828}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But the fun part on the women's side, despite going for eight straight gold medals and having a 58-game Olympic winning streak, there were some tests.\", \"from\": 831, \"to\": 981, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the fun part\", \"from\": 835, \"to\": 847}, {\"ngram\": \"the women's side\", \"from\": 851, \"to\": 867}, {\"ngram\": \"eight straight gold medals\", \"from\": 887, \"to\": 913}, {\"ngram\": \"a 58-game Olympic winning streak\", \"from\": 925, \"to\": 957}, {\"ngram\": \"some tests\", \"from\": 970, \"to\": 980}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That includes Belgium who brought a lot of fans and did advance as the third team in the group.\", \"from\": 982, \"to\": 1077, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 996, \"end\": 1003, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9852058661154357, \"rank\": 0.014298843754124508, \"text\": \"Belgium\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium_national_football_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 1016, \"to\": 1021}, {\"ngram\": \"fans\", \"from\": 1025, \"to\": 1029}, {\"ngram\": \"the third team\", \"from\": 1049, \"to\": 1063}, {\"ngram\": \"the group\", \"from\": 1067, \"to\": 1076}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Germany, they played yesterday, and that was kind of a back-and-forth affair, certainly in the first half.\", \"from\": 1078, \"to\": 1184, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"kind of a back-and-forth affair\", \"from\": 1123, \"to\": 1154}, {\"ngram\": \"the first half\", \"from\": 1169, \"to\": 1183}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They bring a lot of WNBA talent.\", \"from\": 1185, \"to\": 1217, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1205, \"end\": 1209, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_National_Basketball_Association\", \"score\": 0.9999974798270084, \"rank\": 1.591602972547233e-06, \"text\": \"WNBA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_National_Basketball_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_National_Basketball_Association\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 1196, \"to\": 1201}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And then you have the host country in France who will bring the juice and despite a tough loss last night against Australia, should still pose a threat later in the tournament.\", \"from\": 1218, \"to\": 1394, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1256, \"end\": 1262, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9610517773891956, \"rank\": 0.03140452532534923, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the host country\", \"from\": 1236, \"to\": 1252}, {\"ngram\": \"the juice\", \"from\": 1278, \"to\": 1287}, {\"ngram\": \"a tough loss\", \"from\": 1300, \"to\": 1312}, {\"ngram\": \"Australia\", \"from\": 1332, \"to\": 1341}, {\"ngram\": \"a threat\", \"from\": 1361, \"to\": 1369}, {\"ngram\": \"the tournament\", \"from\": 1379, \"to\": 1393}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On the men's side, a French team that has a lot of NBA talent.\", \"from\": 1396, \"to\": 1458, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1447, \"end\": 1450, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"score\": 0.999999547116079, \"rank\": 3.5402826207782607e-07, \"text\": \"NBA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the men's side\", \"from\": 1399, \"to\": 1413}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 1438, \"to\": 1443}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And we have seen them at their top level is going to be a challenge.\", \"from\": 1459, \"to\": 1527, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"their top level\", \"from\": 1484, \"to\": 1499}, {\"ngram\": \"a challenge\", \"from\": 1515, \"to\": 1526}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They get Canada right off the bat.\", \"from\": 1528, \"to\": 1562, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Canada\", \"from\": 1537, \"to\": 1543}, {\"ngram\": \"the bat\", \"from\": 1554, \"to\": 1561}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And we are excited to see what that looks like.\", \"from\": 1563, \"to\": 1610, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Then you have got Germany who is playing incredibly well.\", \"from\": 1611, \"to\": 1668, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1629, \"end\": 1636, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9942962716861897, \"rank\": 0.0032027205412908347, \"text\": \"Germany\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany_national_football_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So we expect there to be some really great match-ups, and we are just excited to be here for it.\", \"from\": 1669, \"to\": 1765, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"some really great match-ups\", \"from\": 1694, \"to\": 1721}]}, {\"sentence\": \"DWYANE WADE: As Noah said, being in Lille, gave all of us the time as a team to be able to -- this is my first time doing this -- it gave us time as a team to be able to spend time together, be around each other in a place that we feel is very charming and have very great people that really helped us accomplish all the things we needed to.\", \"from\": 1767, \"to\": 2108, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1767, \"end\": 1778, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dwyane_Wade\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"DWYANE WADE\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dwyane_Wade\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dwyane_Wade\"}, {\"begin\": 1783, \"end\": 1787, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah\", \"score\": 0.674553830372543, \"rank\": 0.45775427751982106, \"text\": \"Noah\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q43115\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah\"}, {\"begin\": 1803, \"end\": 1808, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lille_OSC\", \"score\": 0.992235290394991, \"rank\": 0.007825319202594803, \"text\": \"Lille\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lille_OSC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lille_OSC\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 1822, \"to\": 1824}, {\"ngram\": \"a team\", \"from\": 1837, \"to\": 1843}, {\"ngram\": \"my first time\", \"from\": 1869, \"to\": 1882}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 1905, \"to\": 1907}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 1908, \"to\": 1912}, {\"ngram\": \"a team\", \"from\": 1916, \"to\": 1922}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 1943, \"to\": 1947}, {\"ngram\": \"a place\", \"from\": 1982, \"to\": 1989}, {\"ngram\": \"very great people\", \"from\": 2029, \"to\": 2046}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 2066, \"to\": 2068}, {\"ngram\": \"all the things\", \"from\": 2080, \"to\": 2094}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I feel like on the court, these teams are doing an incredible job.\", \"from\": 2110, \"to\": 2176, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the court\", \"from\": 2125, \"to\": 2134}, {\"ngram\": \"these teams\", \"from\": 2136, \"to\": 2147}, {\"ngram\": \"an incredible job\", \"from\": 2158, \"to\": 2175}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Not obviously having a lot of time to prepare or even spend together, have been doing an incredible job game by game of meeting the challenge.\", \"from\": 2177, \"to\": 2319, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 2198, \"to\": 2203}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 2207, \"to\": 2211}, {\"ngram\": \"an incredible job game\", \"from\": 2263, \"to\": 2285}, {\"ngram\": \"game\", \"from\": 2289, \"to\": 2293}, {\"ngram\": \"the challenge\", \"from\": 2305, \"to\": 2318}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I think that's the biggest thing.\", \"from\": 2320, \"to\": 2353, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the biggest thing\", \"from\": 2335, \"to\": 2352}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Each game presents its own challenge and they have done an amazing job of meeting the challenge.\", \"from\": 2354, \"to\": 2450, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Each game\", \"from\": 2354, \"to\": 2363}, {\"ngram\": \"its own challenge\", \"from\": 2373, \"to\": 2390}, {\"ngram\": \"an amazing job\", \"from\": 2410, \"to\": 2424}, {\"ngram\": \"the challenge\", \"from\": 2436, \"to\": 2449}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As someone who has played in the Olympics before, now getting to this part, getting to the Paris portion of the program, now is really about locking in even more.\", \"from\": 2452, \"to\": 2614, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2543, \"end\": 2548, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999915705628276, \"rank\": 8.429052579032542e-06, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"someone\", \"from\": 2455, \"to\": 2462}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 2481, \"to\": 2493}, {\"ngram\": \"this part\", \"from\": 2517, \"to\": 2526}, {\"ngram\": \"the program\", \"from\": 2560, \"to\": 2571}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's about locking into the small details even more than before.\", \"from\": 2615, \"to\": 2679, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the small details\", \"from\": 2639, \"to\": 2656}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You get a little bit more serious about it as you get closer to now smelling the weekend coming where a gold medal game is on Saturday.\", \"from\": 2680, \"to\": 2815, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the weekend\", \"from\": 2757, \"to\": 2768}, {\"ngram\": \"a gold medal game\", \"from\": 2782, \"to\": 2799}, {\"ngram\": \"Saturday\", \"from\": 2806, \"to\": 2814}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But also not looking over and looking past anyone.\", \"from\": 2816, \"to\": 2866, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"anyone\", \"from\": 2859, \"to\": 2865}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And obviously Brazil is our first for U.S.A.\", \"from\": 2868, \"to\": 2912, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2882, \"end\": 2888, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil\", \"score\": 0.887688772874105, \"rank\": 0.1182929260152849, \"text\": \"Brazil\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"U.S.A.\", \"from\": 2906, \"to\": 2912}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But not looking past anyone.\", \"from\": 2913, \"to\": 2941, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"anyone\", \"from\": 2934, \"to\": 2940}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And the coaching staff that was put together is going to make sure of that.\", \"from\": 2942, \"to\": 3017, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the coaching staff\", \"from\": 2946, \"to\": 2964}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And the leaders like LeBron and KD and others will make sure.\", \"from\": 3018, \"to\": 3079, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3050, \"end\": 3052, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Knock-down_kit\", \"score\": 0.42409493637828183, \"rank\": 0.777111812993841, \"text\": \"KD\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Knock-down_kit\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Knock-down_kit\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the leaders\", \"from\": 3022, \"to\": 3033}, {\"ngram\": \"LeBron\", \"from\": 3039, \"to\": 3045}, {\"ngram\": \"others\", \"from\": 3057, \"to\": 3063}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So really excited for the guys understanding the feeling that's going on in their minds right now as they prepare with their families started coming in more, with everybody in the U.S. is probably now going to tune in a little bit more as it gets a little closer.\", \"from\": 3081, \"to\": 3344, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the guys\", \"from\": 3103, \"to\": 3111}, {\"ngram\": \"the feeling\", \"from\": 3126, \"to\": 3137}, {\"ngram\": \"their minds\", \"from\": 3157, \"to\": 3168}, {\"ngram\": \"their families\", \"from\": 3200, \"to\": 3214}, {\"ngram\": \"everybody\", \"from\": 3244, \"to\": 3253}, {\"ngram\": \"the U.S.\", \"from\": 3257, \"to\": 3265}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Just really exciting time for basketball and really exciting time for sports.\", \"from\": 3345, \"to\": 3422, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Just really exciting time\", \"from\": 3345, \"to\": 3370}, {\"ngram\": \"basketball\", \"from\": 3375, \"to\": 3385}, {\"ngram\": \"really exciting time\", \"from\": 3390, \"to\": 3410}, {\"ngram\": \"sports\", \"from\": 3415, \"to\": 3421}]}, {\"sentence\": \"LACHINA ROBINSON: I echo Dwyane and Noah's sentiments on Lille.\", \"from\": 3424, \"to\": 3487, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3460, \"end\": 3464, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah\", \"score\": 0.999356943589652, \"rank\": 0.00030369342270708126, \"text\": \"Noah\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q43115\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah\"}, {\"begin\": 3481, \"end\": 3486, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lille_OSC\", \"score\": 0.9453732718942202, \"rank\": 0.056625864120084225, \"text\": \"Lille\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lille_OSC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lille_OSC\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"LACHINA ROBINSON\", \"from\": 3424, \"to\": 3440}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Had a really good time there.\", \"from\": 3488, \"to\": 3517, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a really good time\", \"from\": 3492, \"to\": 3510}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's crazy how fast the two weeks went.\", \"from\": 3518, \"to\": 3557, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the two weeks\", \"from\": 3538, \"to\": 3551}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But the energy for the game of basketball was felt through every game that we called.\", \"from\": 3558, \"to\": 3643, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the energy\", \"from\": 3562, \"to\": 3572}, {\"ngram\": \"the game\", \"from\": 3577, \"to\": 3585}, {\"ngram\": \"basketball\", \"from\": 3589, \"to\": 3599}, {\"ngram\": \"every game\", \"from\": 3617, \"to\": 3627}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On the women's side, I know that Noah spoke to this earlier, but the Belgium game was just one of the best environments I have ever been in as an analyst, and I have been doing this for 17 years.\", \"from\": 3645, \"to\": 3840, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3678, \"end\": 3682, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah\", \"score\": 0.999356943589652, \"rank\": 0.00030369342270708126, \"text\": \"Noah\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q43115\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah\"}, {\"begin\": 3714, \"end\": 3721, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium\", \"score\": 0.6107199178181587, \"rank\": 0.6218179037267375, \"text\": \"Belgium\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the women's side\", \"from\": 3648, \"to\": 3664}, {\"ngram\": \"the best environments\", \"from\": 3743, \"to\": 3764}, {\"ngram\": \"an analyst\", \"from\": 3788, \"to\": 3798}, {\"ngram\": \"17 years\", \"from\": 3831, \"to\": 3839}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And it makes me excited for what we will see now in Paris.\", \"from\": 3841, \"to\": 3899, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3893, \"end\": 3898, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999442870631289, \"rank\": 5.5716040828975075e-05, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And just thinking about the United States and their journey to this point, there is a lot of pressure for a team that's won seven straight gold medals and is going for eight.\", \"f