\": 7402, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"LeBron James\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But she's quick.\", \"from\": 7412, \"to\": 7428, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She's got more energy on both ends of the floor than anyone else.\", \"from\": 7429, \"to\": 7494, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"more energy\", \"from\": 7439, \"to\": 7450}, {\"ngram\": \"both ends\", \"from\": 7454, \"to\": 7463}, {\"ngram\": \"the floor\", \"from\": 7467, \"to\": 7476}, {\"ngram\": \"anyone\", \"from\": 7482, \"to\": 7488}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You almost forget she's 6'5\\\" because of how mobile she is and how great her footwork is around the rim.\", \"from\": 7495, \"to\": 7598, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her footwork\", \"from\": 7567, \"to\": 7579}, {\"ngram\": \"the rim\", \"from\": 7590, \"to\": 7597}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That does not even speak to how she cleans up everything defensively.\", \"from\": 7600, \"to\": 7669, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 7646, \"to\": 7656}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So I have a great level of respect for what she does between the lines because I know how much she has grown and how hard she's worked on her game over time.\", \"from\": 7670, \"to\": 7827, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a great level\", \"from\": 7680, \"to\": 7693}, {\"ngram\": \"respect\", \"from\": 7697, \"to\": 7704}, {\"ngram\": \"the lines\", \"from\": 7731, \"to\": 7740}, {\"ngram\": \"her game\", \"from\": 7808, \"to\": 7816}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 7822, \"to\": 7826}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And as a person, boy, her voice is just really important to the leadership and the advoc