am, you have had multiple guys, even multiple in the game, but you have got multiple guys who have led the charge.\", \"from\": 9244, \"to\": 9382, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this team\", \"from\": 9261, \"to\": 9270}, {\"ngram\": \"multiple guys\", \"from\": 9285, \"to\": 9298}, {\"ngram\": \"the game\", \"from\": 9317, \"to\": 9325}, {\"ngram\": \"multiple guys\", \"from\": 9344, \"to\": 9357}, {\"ngram\": \"the charge\", \"from\": 9371, \"to\": 9381}]}, {\"sentence\": \"One night it's KD.\", \"from\": 9383, \"to\": 9401, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 9398, \"end\": 9400, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christian_Democrats_(Sweden)\", \"score\": 0.7655466376938552, \"rank\": 0.13887671823957143, \"text\": \"KD\", \"types\": [\"Q7278\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christian_Democrats_(Sweden)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christian_Democrats_(Sweden)\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Obviously, LeBron has been consistent.\", \"from\": 9402, \"to\": 9440, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"LeBron\", \"from\": 9413, \"to\": 9419}]}, {\"sentence\": \"One night it's Edwards.\", \"from\": 9441, \"to\": 9464, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Edwards\", \"from\": 9456, \"to\": 9463}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And the list goes on and on.\", \"from\": 9466, \"to\": 9494, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the list\", \"from\": 9470, \"to\": 9478}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There is been multiple different guys, and what I love about it is watching the team enjoy each other's success.\", \"from\": 9495, \"to\": 9607, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"multiple different guys\", \"from\": 9509, \"to\": 9532}, {\"ngram\": \"the team\", \"from\": 9571, \"to\": 9579}, {\"ngram\": \"each other's success\", \"from\": 9586, \"to\": 9606}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Even with all the noise that probably coming from the outside, it looks like from the inside these guys have been just enjoying each other's success.\", \"from\": 9608, \"to\": 9757, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"all the noise\", \"from\": 9618, \"to\": 9631}, {\"ngram\": \"the outside\", \"from\": 9658, \"to\": 9669}, {\"ngram\": \"the inside\", \"from\": 9690, \"to\": 9700}, {\"ngram\": \"these guys\", \"from\": 9701, \"to\": 9711}, {\"ngram\": \"each other's success\", \"from\": 9736, \"to\": 9756}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And we know for a team to be able to be successful they will have to do that.\", \"from\": 9758, \"to\": 9835, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a team\", \"from\": 9774, \"to\": 9780}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And of course, we know that the one part about this is all it takes is one bad quarter, takes one bad game.\", \"from\": 9837, \"to\": 9944, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"course\", \"from\": 9844, \"to\": 9850}, {\"ngram\": \"the one part\", \"from\": 9865, \"to\": 9877}, {\"ngram\": \"one bad quarter\", \"from\": 9908, \"to\": 9923}, {\"ngram\": \"one bad game\", \"from\": 9931, \"to\": 9943}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I have been there before in '06 when we lost.\", \"from\": 9945, \"to\": 9990, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We just had one bad game and we ended up with a bronze.\", \"from\": 9991, \"to\": 10046, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"one bad game\", \"from\": 10003, \"to\": 10015}, {\"ngram\": \"a bronze\", \"from\": 10037, \"to\": 10045}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And it does not mean that we were not better than the field.\", \"from\": 10047, \"to\": 10107, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the field\", \"from\": 10097, \"to\": 10106}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I think the team understands that.\", \"from\": 10109, \"to\": 10143, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the team\", \"from\": 10117, \"to\": 10125}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You can see the way they approached the game as true professionals.\", \"from\": 10144, \"to\": 10211, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the way\", \"from\": 10156, \"to\": 10163}, {\"ngram\": \"the game\", \"from\": 10180, \"to\": 10188}, {\"ngram\": \"true professionals\", \"from\": 10192, \"to\": 10210}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They are still coming out and working their game, finding moments throughout the game to get better and playing, like we keep saying on the air, they have been running through the tape.\", \"from\": 10212, \"to\": 10397, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"their game\", \"from\": 10250, \"to\": 10260}, {\"ngram\": \"moments\", \"from\": 10270, \"to\": 10277}, {\"ngram\": \"the game\", \"from\": 10289, \"to\": 10297}, {\"ngram\": \"the air\", \"from\": 10348, \"to\": 10355}, {\"ngram\": \"the tape\", \"from\": 10388, \"to\": 10396}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That's what you want to see with a team that's probably the most talented, one of the most talented that we have seen in a while.\", \"from\": 10398, \"to\": 10527, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a team\", \"from\": 10431, \"to\": 10437}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We have seen them continue to respect the field, run through the tape, and continue to work their game.\", \"from\": 10528, \"to\": 10631, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the field\", \"from\": 10566, \"to\": 10575}, {\"ngram\": \"the tape\", \"from\": 10589, \"to\": 10597}, {\"ngram\": \"their game\", \"from\": 10620, \"to\": 10630}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's basketball.\", \"from\": 10633, \"to\": 10649, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"basketball\", \"from\": 10638, \"to\": 10648}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A team does not need to be better than you four times out of the seven like the NBA; they have to just be better than you one night.\", \"from\": 10650, \"to\": 10782, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 10730, \"end\": 10733, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"score\": 0.9960824515468306, \"rank\": 0.003932811010212711, \"text\": \"NBA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A team\", \"from\": 10650, \"to\": 10656}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That's the tough part about the Olympics.\", \"from\": 10783, \"to\": 10824, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the tough part\", \"from\": 10790, \"to\": 10804}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 10811, \"to\": 10823}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Obviously, Team USA is preparing for all those things.\", \"from\": 10825, \"to\": 10879, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 10836, \"end\": 10844, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9986003750566522, \"rank\": 0.0008405251804693499, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"all those things\", \"from\": 10862, \"to\": 10878}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And I can guarantee you that they are getting a little bit more disciplined than they probably were.\", \"from\": 10880, \"to\": 10980, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And as they tighten up and tune up for the Games, as we get to now, from the Paris side of things, and understanding exactly that, that a team just needs to be better than you on one night.\", \"from\": 10981, \"to\": 11170, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 11058, \"end\": 11063, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9992420759695049, \"rank\": 0.0007584988460572533, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 11020, \"to\": 1