ade\"}, {\"begin\": 11836, \"end\": 11842, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece\", \"score\": 0.9276053075432514, \"rank\": 0.06354095073954663, \"text\": \"Greece\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the first thing\", \"from\": 11744, \"to\": 11759}, {\"ngram\": \"the names\", \"from\": 11817, \"to\": 11826}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I have never really had to do that, just in my normal life and definitely with the world listening.\", \"from\": 11849, \"to\": 11948, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my normal life\", \"from\": 11893, \"to\": 11907}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 11928, \"to\": 11937}]}, {\"sentence\": \"One thing I have done since I retired is I work with a vocal coach.\", \"from\": 11950, \"to\": 12017, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"One thing\", \"from\": 11950, \"to\": 11959}, {\"ngram\": \"a vocal coach\", \"from\": 12003, \"to\": 12016}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I work with a speech coach as well.\", \"from\": 12018, \"to\": 12053, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a speech coach\", \"from\": 12030, \"to\": 12044}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Just like when I played basketball, I had trainers.\", \"from\": 12054, \"to\": 12105, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"basketball\", \"from\": 12078, \"to\": 12088}, {\"ngram\": \"trainers\", \"from\": 12096, \"to\": 12104}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I have people help me get 1 percent better, understanding that God gave me natural talents but how do you take it to another level?\", \"from\": 12106, \"to\": 12237, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 12113, \"to\": 12119}, {\"ngram\": \"God\", \"from\": 12169, \"to\": 12172}, {\"ngram\": \"natural talents\", \"from\": 12181, \"to\": 12196}, {\"ngram\": \"another level\", \"from\": 12223, \"to\": 12236}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Not knowing this space, I just did what I normally did, and I just prepared myself as much as possible.\", \"from\": 12239, \"to\": 12342, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this space\", \"from\": 12251, \"to\": 12261}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Go and read as much information about each team as I can so I have my own information and knowledge.\", \"from\": 12343, \"to\": 12443, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"as much information\", \"from\": 12355, \"to\": 12374}, {\"ngram\": \"each team\", \"from\": 12381, \"to\": 12390}, {\"ngram\": \"my own information\", \"from\": 12410, \"to\": 12428}, {\"ngram\": \"knowledge\", \"from\": 12433, \"to\": 12442}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Go watch film.\", \"from\": 12444, \"to\": 12458, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"film\", \"from\": 12453, \"to\": 12457}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I watched the games that the U.S.A. played versus a lot of teams in this field and any other film I could find from other teams just so I could be familiar with their game.\", \"from\": 12459, \"to\": 12631, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the games\", \"from\": 12469, \"to\": 12478}, {\"ngram\": \"the U.S.A.\", \"from\": 12484, \"to\": 12494}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 12509, \"to\": 12514}, {\"ngram\": \"teams\", \"from\": 12518, \"to\": 12523}, {\"ngram\": \"this field\", \"from\": 12527, \"to\": 12537}, {\"ngram\": \"any other film\", \"from\": 12542, \"to\": 12556}, {\"ngram\": \"other teams\", \"from\": 12575, \"to\": 12586}, {\"ngram\": \"their game\", \"from\": 12620, \"to\": 12630}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And then from there, like I said, spend a lot of time around the team.\", \"from\": 12633, \"to\": 12703, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 12673, \"to\": 12678}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 12682, \"to\": 12686}, {\"ngram\": \"the team\", \"from\": 12694, \"to\": 12702}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Noah is an Encyclopedia of knowledge when it comes to all sports but definitely this sport.\", \"from\": 12704, \"to\": 12795, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 12704, \"end\": 12708, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah\", \"score\": 0.9998291734606393, \"rank\": 7.628679854695672e-05, \"text\": \"Noah\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q43115\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an Encyclopedia\", \"from\": 12712, \"to\": 12727}, {\"ngram\": \"knowledge\", \"from\": 12731, \"to\": 12740}, {\"ngram\": \"all sports\", \"from\": 12758, \"to\": 12768}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Just sitting around, listening, asking a lot of questions, not being afraid to say what I do not know.\", \"from\": 12796, \"to\": 12898, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 12835, \"to\": 12840}, {\"ngram\": \"questions\", \"from\": 12844, \"to\": 12853}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But most importantly just being myself.\", \"from\": 12899, \"to\": 12938, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That's the one thing that everyone told me and that's what I told myself when I signed up to do this was I am going to bring my brand of basketball to the airwaves, understanding, just like in life, some people are going to love it.\", \"from\": 12939, \"to\": 13171, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the one thing\", \"from\": 12946, \"to\": 12959}, {\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 12965, \"to\": 12973}, {\"ngram\": \"my brand\", \"from\": 13064, \"to\": 13072}, {\"ngram\": \"basketball\", \"from\": 13076, \"to\": 13086}, {\"ngram\": \"the airwaves\", \"from\": 13090, \"to\": 13102}, {\"ngram\": \"understanding\", \"from\": 13104, \"to\": 13117}, {\"ngram\": \"life\", \"from\": 13132, \"to\": 13136}, {\"ngram\": \"some people\", \"from\": 13138, \"to\": 13149}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Some people will not love it.\", \"from\": 13172, \"to\": 13201, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Some people\", \"from\": 13172, \"to\": 13183}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But that's just the nature of life and that's the nature of the game.\", \"from\": 13202, \"to\": 13271, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"just the nature\", \"from\": 13213, \"to\": 13228}, {\"ngram\": \"life\", \"from\": 13232, \"to\": 13236}, {\"ngram\": \"the nature\", \"from\": 13248, \"to\": 13258}, {\"ngram\": \"the game\", \"from\": 13262, \"to\": 13270}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Also, too to have fun with it but also bring a player's perspective.\", \"from\": 13273, \"to\": 13341, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"fun\", \"from\": 13291, \"to\": 13294}, {\"ngram\": \"a player's perspective\", \"from\": 13318, \"to\": 13340}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I have been on the court before.\", \"from\": 13342, \"to\": 13374, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the court\", \"from\": 13357, \"to\": 13366}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I have been in the huddles before.\", \"from\": 13375, \"to\": 13409, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the huddles\", \"from\": 13390, \"to\": 13401}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I understand kind of what the Olympic athletes are dealing with and growing through.\", \"from\": 13410, \"to\": 13494, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympic athletes\", \"from\": 13436, \"to\": 13456}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So just bringing that perspective to the table that not a lot of people could bring to the table.\", \"from\": 13495, \"to\": 13592, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that perspective\", \"from\": 13512, \"to\": 13528}, {\"ngram\": \"the table\", \"from\": 13532, \"to\": 13541}, {\"ngram\": \"not a lot\", \"from\": 13547, \"to\": 13556}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 13560, \"to\": 13566}, {\"ngram\": \"the table\", \"from\": 13582, \"to\": 13591}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So understanding that and being confident in that.\", \"from\": 13593, \"to\": 13643, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That was kind of my prep.\", \"from\": 13645, \"to\": 13670, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"kind of my prep\", \"from\": 13654, \"to\": 13669}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And then from there my prep has continued to be the same.\", \"from\": 13671, \"to\": 13728, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my prep\", \"from\": 13691, \"to\": 13698}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We just spent a lot of time together in Lille as we said when we came on this call.\", \"from\": 13729, \"to\": 13812, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 13769, \"end\": 13774, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lille_OSC\", \"score\": 0.661020385808057, \"rank\": 0.5128038569238391, \"text\": \"Lille\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lille_OSC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lille_OSC\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 13743, \"to\": 13748}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 13752, \"to\": 13756}, {\"ngram\": \"this call\", \"from\": 13802, \"to\": 13811}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And I think that was good for all of us just to be together and just get to know each other.\", \"from\": 13813, \"to\": 13905, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 13850, \"to\": 13852}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And as you heard at the end of our games, some of the games we were able to talk about Xs and Os and give information about what we were watching.\", \"from\": 13906, \"to\": 14052, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 13926, \"to\": 13933}, {\"ngram\": \"our games\", \"from\": 13937, \"to\": 13946}, {\"ngram\": \"the games\", \"from\": 13956, \"to\": 13965}, {\"ngram\": \"Xs\", \"from\": 13993, \"to\": 13995}, {\"ngram\": \"information\", \"from\": 14012, \"to\": 14023}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And some of them we are putting culture, movie references up.\", \"from\": 14053, \"to\": 14114, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"culture\", \"from\": 14085, \"to\": 14092}, {\"ngram\": \"movie references\", \"from\": 14094, \"to\": 14110}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We are talking about comedians, doing all kinds of things to fill the airwaves as well.\", \"from\": 14115, \"to\": 14202, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"comedians\", \"from\": 14136, \"to\": 14145}, {\"ngram\": \"all kinds\", \"from\": 14153, \"to\": 14162}, {\"ngram\": \"things\", \"from\": 14166, \"to\": 14172}, {\"ngram\": \"the airwaves\", \"from\": 14181, \"to\": 14193}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That shows the connection between either Noah and LaChina or Noah and myself and how we see this brand of basketball feeling and looking.\", \"from\": 14204, \"to\": 14341, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 14245, \"end\": 14249, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah\", \"score\": 0.6669642259050832, \"rank\": 0.4254808116935193, \"text\": \"Noah\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q43115\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah\"}, {\"begin\": 14265, \"end\": 14269, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah\", \"score\": 0.6669642259050832, \"rank\": 0.4254808116935193, \"text\": \"Noah\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q43115\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the connection\", \"from\": 14215, \"to\": 14229}, {\"ngram\": \"LaChina\", \"from\": 14254, \"to\": 14261}, {\"ngram\": \"this brand\", \"from\": 14296, \"to\": 14306}, {\"ngram\": \"basketball feeling\", \"from\": 14310, \"to\": 14328}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So we are trying to bring the audience into Pierre Mauroy Stadium even though they may hear it, they may be able to see it from the TV, but they can feel it even more coming from us.\", \"from\": 14342, \"to\": 14524, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the audience\", \"from\": 14368, \"to\": 14380}, {\"ngram\": \"Pierre Mauroy Stadium\", \"from\": 14386, \"to\": 14407}, {\"ngram\": \"the TV\", \"from\": 14470, \"to\": 14476}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 14521, \"to\": 14523}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I think we did a good job of bringing them in the stadium and watching the game with us.\", \"from\": 14525, \"to\": 14613, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a good job\", \"from\": 14540, \"to\": 14550}, {\"ngram\": \"the stadium\", \"from\": 14571, \"to\": 14582}, {\"ngram\": \"the game\", \"from\": 14596, \"to\": 14604}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 14610, \"to\": 14612}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Q.Is there anything you thought would be harder as a transition with all this in terms of being easier?\", \"from\": 14615, \"to\": 14718, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 14626, \"to\": 14634}, {\"ngram\": \"a transition\", \"from\": 14666, \"to\": 14678}, {\"ngram\": \"terms\", \"from\": 14696, \"to\": 14701}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And vice versa, is there something that's easier?\", \"from\": 14719, \"to\": 14768, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 14744, \"to\": 14753}]}, {\"sentence\": \"DWYANE WADE: Well, whenever you are doing something that you have never done before, you are going to think about everything that could go wrong.\", \"from\": 14770, \"to\": 14915, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 14770, \"end\": 14781, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dwyane_Wade\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"DWYANE WADE\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dwyane_Wade\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dwyane_Wade\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 14812, \"to\": 14821}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 14884, \"to\": 14894}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You are going to have anxiety, some anxiousness in there as well.\", \"from\": 14916, \"to\": 14981, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"anxiety\", \"from\": 14938, \"to\": 14945}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's going to be a challenge to you.\", \"from\": 14982, \"to\": 15018, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a challenge\", \"from\": 14999, \"to\": 15010}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So all those things have been true.\", \"from\": 15019, \"to\": 15054, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"all those things\", \"from\": 15022, \"to\": 15038}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I definitely know that I have not even scratched the surface of the understanding of all the things.\", \"from\": 15056, \"to\": 15156, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the surface\", \"from\": 15105, \"to\": 15116}, {\"ngram\": \"the understanding\", \"from\": 15120, \"to\": 15137}, {\"ngram\": \"all the things\", \"from\": 15141, \"to\": 15155}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I have not even used a telestrator yet.\", \"from\": 15157, \"to\": 15196, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a telestrator\", \"from\": 15178, \"to\": 15191}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And that's coming up, I heard.\", \"from\": 15197, \"to\": 15227, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There are so many things to learn even having a producer in your ear, knowing when to talk, knowing when to let it breathe and knowing when to let the crowd bring the energy.\", \"from\": 15228, \"to\": 15402, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"so many things\", \"from\": 15238, \"to\": 15252}, {\"ngram\": \"a producer\", \"from\": 15274, \"to\": 15284}, {\"ngram\": \"your ear\", \"from\": 15288, \"to\": 15296}, {\"ngram\": \"the crowd\", \"from\": 15375, \"to\": 15384}, {\"ngram\": \"the energy\", \"from\": 15391, \"to\": 15401}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There is things I am learning along the way.\", \"from\": 15403, \"to\": 15447, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"things\", \"from\": 15412, \"to\": 15418}, {\"ngram\": \"the way\", \"from\": 15439, \"to\": 15446}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Like I said, and I told the team when I first signed up to this, one thing I have always been in my life, I have always tried to be coachable, even though I am someone who listens to my coaches, then I respond.\", \"from\": 15449, \"to\": 15659, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the team\", \"from\": 15473, \"to\": 15481}, {\"ngram\": \"my life\", \"from\": 15546, \"to\": 15553}, {\"ngram\": \"someone\", \"from\": 15609, \"to\": 15616}, {\"ngram\": \"my coaches\", \"from\": 15632, \"to\": 15642}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I do talk back.\", \"from\": 15660, \"to\": 15675, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But I am very coachable as well.\", \"from\": 15676, \"to\": 15708, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"To be able to have individuals around me to my left and right, in my ear, giving me information that I need to be my best self so we can obviously be our best selves.\", \"from\": 15709, \"to\": 15875, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"individuals\", \"from\": 15728, \"to\": 15739}, {\"ngram\": \"my left\", \"from\": 15753, \"to\": 15760}, {\"ngram\": \"my ear\", \"from\": 15775, \"to\": 15781}, {\"ngram\": \"information\", \"from\": 15793, \"to\": 15804}, {\"ngram\": \"my best self\", \"from\": 15823, \"to\": 15835}, {\"ngram\": \"our best selves\", \"from\": 15859, \"to\": 15874}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So, yeah, I hope that answers your question.\", \"from\": 15877, \"to\": 15921, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your question\", \"from\": 15907, \"to\": 15920}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Q.Ms.\", \"from\": 15923, \"to\": 15928, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Q.Ms\", \"from\": 15923, \"to\": 15927}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Robinson and Mr. Wade, you both talked about the importance of chemistry and of leadership on these teams, both the men's and women's.\", \"from\": 15929, \"to\": 16063, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": 