}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I think what I have noticed in the three games that the United States women have played is that there is always been a stretch where another team goes on a run and there has to be a response.\", \"from\": 16437, \"to\": 16628, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 16493, \"end\": 16506, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9942609958599633, \"rank\": 0.00468841908799614, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the three games\", \"from\": 16468, \"to\": 16483}, {\"ngram\": \"a stretch\", \"from\": 16554, \"to\": 16563}, {\"ngram\": \"another team\", \"from\": 16570, \"to\": 16582}, {\"ngram\": \"a run\", \"from\": 16591, \"to\": 16596}, {\"ngram\": \"a response\", \"from\": 16617, \"to\": 16627}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And that's the moment where -- I am sure Dwyane can speak to this and his experience; my playing experience is nothing compared to his -- but when you look around at your teammates and everyone's wondering who is going to step up or who's going to make that next play or who is going to do something to change the momentum of the game -- we saw that when Japan got hot hitting 3s.\", \"from\": 16630, \"to\": 17010, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 16985, \"end\": 16990, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_women's_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.5490325124089659, \"rank\": 0.6324558597888739, \"text\": \"Japan\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_women's_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_women's_national_football_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the moment\", \"from\": 16641, \"to\": 16651}, {\"ngram\": \"Dwyane\", \"from\": 16671, \"to\": 16677}, {\"ngram\": \"my playing experience\", \"from\": 16716, \"to\": 16737}, {\"ngra