hat's something we have all seen is that even though they are all talented, want to be playing, the fact that they are cheering for each other, no matter who is on the floor, no matter who is making the play or the bucket, I think that adds to the chemistry as well.\", \"from\": 20021, \"to\": 20295, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 20035, \"to\": 20044}, {\"ngram\": \"the floor\", \"from\": 20193, \"to\": 20202}, {\"ngram\": \"the play\", \"from\": 20228, \"to\": 20236}, {\"ngram\": \"the bucket\", \"from\": 20240, \"to\": 20250}, {\"ngram\": \"the chemistry\", \"from\": 20273, \"to\": 20286}]}, {\"sentence\": \"DWYANE WADE: Just as I said, the unity, that we look for, especially LaChina and I.\", \"from\": 20297, \"to\": 20380, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 20297, \"end\": 20308, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dwyane_Wade\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"DWYANE WADE\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dwyane_Wade\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dwyane_Wade\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the unity\", \"from\": 20326, \"to\": 20335}, {\"ngram\": \"especially LaChina\", \"from\": 20355, \"to\": 20373}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Unfortunately Noah did not play basketball probably after grade school, (laughter) but as former athletes we look at the unity that the team has in those moments where they are not being as successful, you look at them how they are cheering for each other, you look at the conversations, the side conversations they have and the celebrations they are all doing together, the LeBron flex, when LeBron does something -- these guys are all connected and unified.\", \"from\": 20381, \"to\": 20840, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 20395, \"end\": 20399, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah\", \"score\": 0.9863988312908301, \"rank\": 0.0047643877223012, \"text\": \"Noah\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q43115\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"basketball\", \"from\": 20413, \"to\": 20423}, {\"ngram\": \"grade school\", \"from\": 20439, \"to\": 20451}, {\"ngram\": \"laughter\", \"from\": 20454, \"to\": 20462}, {\"ngram\": \"former athletes\", \"from\": 20471, \"to\": 20486}, {\"ngram\": \"the unity\", \"from\": 20498, \"to\": 20507}, {\"ngram\": \"the team\", \"from\": 20513, \"to\": 20521}, {\"ngram\": \"those moments\", \"from\": 20529, \"to\": 20542}, {\"ngram\": \"the conversations\", \"from\": 20650, \"to\": 20667}, {\"ngram\": \"the side conversations\", \"from\": 20669, \"to\": 20691}, {\"ngram\": \"the celebrations\", \"from\": 20706, \"to\": 20722}, {\"ngram\": \"the LeBron flex\", \"from\": 20752, \"to\": 20767}, {\"ngram\": \"LeBron\", \"from\": 20774, \"to\": 20780}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 20786, \"to\": 20795}, {\"ngram\": \"these guys\", \"from\": 20799, \"to\": 20809}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The chef Curry cooking you up.\", \"from\": 20842, \"to\": 20872, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The chef\", \"from\": 20842, \"to\": 20850}, {\"ngram\": \"Curry\", \"from\": 20851, \"to\": 20856}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You see these guys not only having fun but you see these guys have fun with each other.\", \"from\": 20873, \"to\": 20960, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"these guys\", \"from\": 20881, \"to\": 20891}, {\"ngram\": \"fun\", \"from\": 20908, \"to\": 20911}, {\"ngram\": \"these guys\", \"from\": 20924, \"to\": 20934}, {\"ngram\": \"fun\", \"from\": 20940, \"to\": 20943}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And also, too, being able to coach each other on the floor.\", \"from\": 20961, \"to\": 21020, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the floor\", \"from\": 21010, \"to\": 21019}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I think those are the things that we look at and we see these teams growing with that.\", \"from\": 21021, \"to\": 21107, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the things\", \"from\": 21039, \"to\": 21049}, {\"ngram\": \"these teams\", \"from\": 21077, \"to\": 21088}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Q.Dwyane, obviously you have not done this for a long time, but you are getting reps at the highest levels of broadcasting, obviously working for NBC and calling the Olympics.\", \"from\": 21109, \"to\": 21284, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 21255, \"end\": 21258, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"score\": 0.9387237678754625, \"rank\": 0.035499077904146914, \"text\": \"NBC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a long time\", \"from\": 21156, \"to\": 21167}, {\"ngram\": \"reps\", \"from\": 21189, \"to\": 21193}, {\"ngram\": \"the highest levels\", \"from\": 21197, \"to\": 21215}, {\"ngram\": \"broadcasting\", \"from\": 21219, \"to\": 21231}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 21271, \"to\": 21283}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Have you thought about at all if this is something you want to do full time heading forward?\", \"from\": 21285, \"to\": 21377, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 21326, \"to\": 21335}, {\"ngram\": \"full time\", \"from\": 21351, \"to\": 21360}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And if so, I'd love to just sort of get a sense of maybe this experience has sort of prompted something in you that, hey, I might be good at this or this might be something really interesting to me?\", \"from\": 21378, \"to\": 21576, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a sense\", \"from\": 21418, \"to\": 21425}, {\"ngram\": \"this experience\", \"from\": 21435, \"to\": 21450}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 21472, \"to\": 21481}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 21541, \"to\": 21550}]}, {\"sentence\": \"DWYANE WADE: I think for me is, even when I got the opportunity, when I got asked to do this, I looked at this as probably one of the biggest challenges in my 2024 calendar year.\", \"from\": 21578, \"to\": 21756, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the opportunity\", \"from\": 21626, \"to\": 21641}, {\"ngram\": \"the biggest challenges\", \"from\": 21708, \"to\": 21730}, {\"ngram\": \"my 2024 calendar year\", \"from\": 21734, \"to\": 21755}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The one thing, as a former athlete, you do not find these certain challenges that present themselves every day besides the challenge of life.\", \"from\": 21757, \"to\": 21898, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The one thing\", \"from\": 21757, \"to\": 21770}, {\"ngram\": \"a former athlete\", \"from\": 21775, \"to\": 21791}, {\"ngram\": \"these certain challenges\", \"from\": 21809, \"to\": 21833}, {\"ngram\": \"the challenge\", \"from\": 21876, \"to\": 21889}, {\"ngram\": \"life\", \"from\": 21893, \"to\": 21897}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So this was a big challenge.\", \"from\": 21900, \"to\": 21928, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a big challenge\", \"from\": 21912, \"to\": 21927}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I decided to dive into it, understanding that it was going to be a lot of things that was going to be need to be learned actually on the fly.\", \"from\": 21929, \"to\": 22070, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 21994, \"to\": 21999}, {\"ngram\": \"things\", \"from\": 22003, \"to\": 22009}, {\"ngram\": \"the fly\", \"from\": 22062, \"to\": 22069}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But that's kind of how I live my life.\", \"from\": 22071, \"to\": 22109, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my life\", \"from\": 22101, \"to\": 22108}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If anybody knows anything about me, I just dive into things.\", \"from\": 22110, \"to\": 22170, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"anybody\", \"from\": 22113, \"to\": 22120}, {\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 22127, \"to\": 22135}, {\"ngram\": \"things\", \"from\": 22163, \"to\": 22169}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And so I am in the moment.\", \"from\": 22172, \"to\": 22198, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the moment\", \"from\": 22187, \"to\": 22197}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am definitely asking questions that I do not have the answer to.\", \"from\": 22199, \"to\": 22265, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"questions\", \"from\": 22222, \"to\": 22231}, {\"ngram\": \"the answer\", \"from\": 22251, \"to\": 22261}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Being able to sit right next to Noah and being able to go to dinner and being able to hang out the way we have, I have definitely asked him a lot of questions about this world, stuff that I did not know.\", \"from\": 22266, \"to\": 22469, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 22298, \"end\": 22302, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah\", \"score\": 0.9860782299737557, \"rank\": 0.005261980913230496, \"text\": \"Noah\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q43115\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"dinner\", \"from\": 22327, \"to\": 22333}, {\"ngram\": \"the way\", \"from\": 22361, \"to\": 22368}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 22406, \"to\": 22411}, {\"ngram\": \"questions\", \"from\": 22415, \"to\": 22424}, {\"ngram\": \"this world\", \"from\": 22431, \"to\": 22441}, {\"ngram\": \"stuff\", \"from\": 22443, \"to\": 22448}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Something as simple as, hey, bro, what does number one mean?\", \"from\": 22470, \"to\": 22530, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"bro\", \"from\": 22499, \"to\": 22502}]}, {\"sentence\": \"What is number one team?\", \"from\": 22531, \"to\": 22555, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"number one team\", \"from\": 22539, \"to\": 22554}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I do not know those things.\", \"from\": 22556, \"to\": 22583, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"those things\", \"from\": 22570, \"to\": 22582}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Even though I kind of know I wanted to get a breakdown of it all.\", \"from\": 22584, \"to\": 22649, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a breakdown\", \"from\": 22627, \"to\": 22638}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I just want to enjoy this.\", \"from\": 22650, \"to\": 22676, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"LaChina, Noah and I, we have the best seat in the house.\", \"from\": 22678, \"to\": 22734, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 22687, \"end\": 22691, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah\", \"score\": 0.9860782299737557, \"rank\": 0.005261980913230496, \"text\": \"Noah\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q43115\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the best seat\", \"from\": 22707, \"to\": 22720}, {\"ngram\": \"the house\", \"from\": 22724, \"to\": 22733}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I keep saying this, we literally get to sit center stage and watch the greatest athletes in the sport that we love in basketball compete.\", \"from\": 22735, \"to\": 22872, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"center stage\", \"from\": 22779, \"to\": 22791}, {\"ngram\": \"the greatest athletes\", \"from\": 22802, \"to\": 22823}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 22827, \"to\": 22836}, {\"ngram\": \"basketball compete\", \"from\": 22853, \"to\": 22871}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And we do not get to see them competing at this level, not with this kind of talent.\", \"from\": 22873, \"to\": 22957, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this level\", \"from\": 22916, \"to\": 22926}, {\"ngram\": \"this kind\", \"from\": 22937, \"to\": 22946}, {\"ngram\": \"talent\", \"from\": 22950, \"to\": 22956}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We have been able to be in one of the greatest environments we have ever been around in Pierre-Mauroy Stadium, the energy in the building, the atmosphere has been crazy.\", \"from\": 22959, \"to\": 23128, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the greatest environments\", \"from\": 22993, \"to\": 23018}, {\"ngram\": \"Pierre-Mauroy Stadium\", \"from\": 23047, \"to\": 23068}, {\"ngram\": \"the energy\", \"from\": 23070, \"to\": 23080}, {\"ngram\": \"the building\", \"from\": 23084, \"to\": 23096}, {\"ngram\": \"the atmosphere\", \"from\": 23098, \"to\": 23112}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This is our last week doing this together.\", \"from\": 23129, \"to\": 23171, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our last week\", \"from\": 23137, \"to\": 23150}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I do not want to look too far ahead.\", \"from\": 23172, \"to\": 23208, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I want to enjoy the moment we are in and continue to try to get better, because as Kobe Bryant said, very famous quote, \\\"The job's not done.\\\"\", \"from\": 23210, \"to\": 23351, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 23293, \"end\": 23304, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kobe_Bryant\", \"score\": 0.9999898335096957, \"rank\": 1.0166593634701672e-05, \"text\": \"Kobe Bryant\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kobe_Bryant\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kobe_Bryant\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the moment\", \"from\": 23226, \"to\": 23236}, {\"ngram\": \"very famous quote\", \"from\": 23311, \"to\": 23328}, {\"ngram\": \"The job\", \"from\": 23331, \"to\": 23338}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The job is not finished over here.\", \"from\": 23352, \"to\": 23386, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The job\", \"from\": 23352, \"to\": 23359}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We have a lot of work to do.\", \"from\": 23387, \"to\": 23415, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 23395, \"to\": 23400}, {\"ngram\": \"work\", \"from\": 23404, \"to\": 23408}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We want to keep bringing the same energy and the same education and knowledge to the listeners.\", \"from\": 23416, \"to\": 23511, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the same energy\", \"from\": 23441, \"to\": 23456}, {\"ngram\": \"the same education\", \"from\": 23461, \"to\": 23479}, {\"ngram\": \"knowledge\", \"from\": 23484, \"to\": 23493}, {\"ngram\": \"the listeners\", \"from\": 23497, \"to\": 23510}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Q.Noah, so far, your young broadcasting career has been doing mostly stuff in the U.S.\", \"from\": 23513, \"to\": 23599, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Q.Noah\", \"from\": 23513, \"to\": 23519}, {\"ngram\": \"your young broadcasting career\", \"from\": 23529, \"to\": 23559}, {\"ngram\": \"stuff\", \"from\": 23582, \"to\": 23587}, {\"ngram\": \"the U.S.\", \"from\": 23591, \"to\": 23599}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This summer you have had a case of international broadcasting, first at Roland-Garros with the French Open and now with the Olympics and here and now.\", \"from\": 23600, \"to\": 23750, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a case\", \"from\": 23625, \"to\": 23631}, {\"ngram\": \"international broadcasting\", \"from\": 23635, \"to\": 23661}, {\"ngram\": \"Roland-Garros\", \"from\": 23672, \"to\": 23685}, {\"ngram\": \"the French Open\", \"from\": 23691, \"to\": 23706}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 23720, \"to\": 23732}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I want to ask, how has your Olympic experience been and what's it been like doing broadcasting over in Paris a lot this summer as opposed to doing it in the United States like you are used to?\", \"from\": 23751, \"to\": 23943, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 23854, \"end\": 23859, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999575248335663, \"rank\": 4.247697060058264e-05, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/r