"to\": 24149}, {\"ngram\": \"a half\", \"from\": 24154, \"to\": 24160}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And I am not even close.\", \"from\": 24192, \"to\": 24216, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I feel like half a failure in that sense.\", \"from\": 24217, \"to\": 24258, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"half a failure\", \"from\": 24229, \"to\": 24243}, {\"ngram\": \"that sense\", \"from\": 24247, \"to\": 24257}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But from the broadcasting sense, it's been an incredible experience.\", \"from\": 24260, \"to\": 24328, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the broadcasting sense\", \"from\": 24269, \"to\": 24291}, {\"ngram\": \"an incredible experience\", \"from\": 24303, \"to\": 24327}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I got to do the Notre Dame game last year against Navy in Dublin.\", \"from\": 24329, \"to\": 24394, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 24379, \"end\": 24383, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Navy_Midshipmen_football\", \"score\": 0.9915624691889164, \"rank\": 0.007052542352483068, \"text\": \"Navy\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Navy_Midshipmen_football\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Navy_Midshipmen_football\"}, {\"begin\": 24387, \"end\": 24393, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dublin\", \"score\": 0.9157741059622956, \"rank\": 0.09165849312867899, \"text\": \"Dublin\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dublin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dublin\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Notre Dame game\", \"from\": 24341, \"to\": 24360}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That was my first appetizer to international sports and the fandom that it brings.\", \"from\": 24395, \"to\": 24477, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my first appetizer\", \"from\": 24404, \"to\": 24422}, {\"ngram\": \"international sports\", \"from\": 24426, \"to\": 24446}, {\"ngram\": \"the fandom\", \"from\": 24451, \"to\": 24461}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's a different level of passion and I think we really experienced it.\", \"from\": 24478, \"to\": 24549, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a different level\", \"from\": 24483, \"to\": 24500}, {\"ngram\": \"passion\", \"from\": 24504, \"to\": 24511}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I know Dwyane and LaChina have both been talking about the crowds from last week, whether it was the Belgium and U.S. game or any France men's game we got to do, and certainly the U.S. on both sides.\", \"from\": 24551, \"to\": 24750, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 24652, \"end\": 24659, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium\", \"score\": 0.9939483146763677, \"rank\": 0.006047372962123538, \"text\": \"Belgium\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium\"}, {\"begin\": 24664, \"end\": 24668, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9987266936729089, \"rank\": 0.0011278234411814074, \"text\": \"U.S.\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 24681, \"end\": 24687, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9909773732518571, \"rank\": 0.006837665095199988, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Dwyane\", \"from\": 24558, \"to\": 24564}, {\"ngram\": \"LaChina\", \"from\": 24569, \"to\": 24576}, {\"ngram\": \"the crowds\", \"from\": 24606, \"to\": 24616}, {\"ngram\": \"last week\", \"from\": 24622, \"to\": 24631}, {\"ngram\": \"both sides\", \"from\": 24739, \"to\": 24749}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It just brought out the best in every fan.\", \"from\": 24751, \"to\": 24793, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"every fan\", \"from\": 24783, \"to\": 24792}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And that's what you get, I feel like, when you leave and especially when it's a United States-based sport; basketball and the NBA and the WNBA are considered the best leagues.\", \"from\": 24795, \"to\": 24970, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 24921, \"end\": 24924, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"score\": 0.9999815365791055, \"rank\": 1.107108581843133e-05, \"text\": \"NBA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\"}, {\"begin\": 24933, \"end\": 24937, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_National_Basketball_Association\", \"score\": 0.9999991814446443, \"rank\": 7.485342708368608e-07, \"text\": \"WNBA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_National_Basketball_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_National_Basketball_Association\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a United States-based sport\", \"from\": 24873, \"to\": 24900}, {\"ngram\": \"basketball\", \"from\": 24902, \"to\": 24912}, {\"ngram\": \"the best leagues\", \"from\": 24953, \"to\": 24969}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You get great leagues elsewhere, but these are the best athletes now coming together on international soil.\", \"from\": 24971, \"to\": 25078, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"great leagues\", \"from\": 24979, \"to\": 24992}, {\"ngram\": \"the best athletes\", \"from\": 25018, \"to\": 25035}, {\"ngram\": \"international soil\", \"from\": 25059, \"to\": 25077}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When you get that, you get this different level of fandom and passion.\", \"from\": 25079, \"to\": 25149, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this different level\", \"from\": 25106, \"to\": 25126}, {\"ngram\": \"fandom\", \"from\": 25130, \"to\": 25136}, {\"ngram\": \"passion\", \"from\": 25141, \"to\": 25148}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I think we felt that.\", \"from\": 25151, \"to\": 25172, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's been really, really cool to feel that myself.\", \"from\": 25173, \"to\": 25223, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I got to do Roland-Garros in 2020 when it was COVID.\", \"from\": 25224, \"to\": 25276, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Roland-Garros\", \"from\": 25236, \"to\": 25249}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And so they were only allowing, I think, about a thousand or 2,000 fans total into the grounds.\", \"from\": 25277, \"to\": 25372, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"about a thousand or 2,000 fans\", \"from\": 25318, \"to\": 25348}, {\"ngram\": \"the grounds\", \"from\": 25360, \"to\": 25371}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was amazing to be here and to eat a lot of baguettes and croissants and put on a couple of pounds.\", \"from\": 25374, \"to\": 25475, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 25411, \"to\": 25416}, {\"ngram\": \"baguettes\", \"from\": 25420, \"to\": 25429}, {\"ngram\": \"croissants\", \"from\": 25434, \"to\": 25444}, {\"ngram\": \"a couple\", \"from\": 25456, \"to\": 25464}, {\"ngram\": \"pounds\", \"from\": 25468, \"to\": 25474}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I was really missing that flare that you get with the actual tournament but come back and have it full force is amazing.\", \"from\": 25476, \"to\": 25596, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that flare\", \"from\": 25497, \"to\": 25507}, {\"ngram\": \"the actual tournament\", \"from\": 25526, \"to\": 25547}, {\"ngram\": \"full force\", \"from\": 25574, \"to\": 25584}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This has been kind of the cherry on top.\", \"from\": 25597, \"to\": 25637, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the cherry\", \"from\": 25619, \"to\": 25629}, {\"ngram\": \"top\", \"from\": 25633, \"to\": 25636}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Excited for this final week.\", \"from\": 25638, \"to\": 25666, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this final week\", \"from\": 25650, \"to\": 25665}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Q.LaChina, when the U.S. women's team was announced, one of the reports about why Caitlin Clark and Angel Reese did not make the team was because the tryouts made during the NCAA women's basketball championship, during March Madness.\", \"from\": 25668, \"to\": 25901, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 25750, \"end\": 25763, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caitlin_Clark\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Caitlin Clark\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caitlin_Clark\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caitlin_Clark\"}, {\"begin\": 25768, \"end\": 25779, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angel_Reese\", \"score\": 0.9999717897218395, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Angel Reese\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angel_Reese\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angel_Reese\"}, {\"begin\": 25842, \"end\": 25846, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NCAA_Division_I_Women's_Basketball_Tournament\", \"score\": 0.7324571328072097, \"rank\": 0.3161487082597327, \"text\": \"NCAA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NCAA_Division_I_Women's_Basketball_Tournament\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NCAA_Division_I_Women's_Basketball_Tournament\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Q.LaChina\", \"from\": 25668, \"to\": 25677}, {\"ngram\": \"the U.S. women's team\", \"from\": 25684, \"to\": 25705}, {\"ngram\": \"the reports\", \"from\": 25728, \"to\": 25739}, {\"ngram\": \"the team\", \"from\": 25793, \"to\": 25801}, {\"ngram\": \"March Madness\", \"from\": 25887, \"to\": 25900}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They had no chance to even try out.\", \"from\": 25902, \"to\": 25937, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"no chance\", \"from\": 25911, \"to\": 25920}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Fast forward to 2028, do you think the U.S. Olympic Committee, U.S.A. Basketball, will change the tryout dates so that the next generation Caitlin Clark or Angel Reese, if they want to try out for the team in Los Angeles, they will have a shot?\", \"from\": 25938, \"to\": 26182, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 26077, \"end\": 26090, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caitlin_Clark\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Caitlin Clark\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caitlin_Clark\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caitlin_Clark\"}, {\"begin\": 26094, \"end\": 26105, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angel_Reese\", \"score\": 0.9999717897218395, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Angel Reese\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angel_Reese\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angel_Reese\"}, {\"begin\": 26147, \"end\": 26158, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.9998267312959795, \"rank\": 0.00015298167897348462, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the U.S. Olympic Committee\", \"from\": 25973, \"to\": 25999}, {\"ngram\": \"U.S.A. Basketball\", \"from\": 26001, \"to\": 26018}, {\"ngram\": \"the tryout dates\", \"from\": 26032, \"to\": 26048}, {\"ngram\": \"the next generation\", \"from\": 26057, \"to\": 26076}, {\"ngram\": \"the team\", \"from\": 26135, \"to\": 26143}, {\"ngram\": \"a shot\", \"from\": 26175, \"to\": 26181}]}, {\"sentence\": \"LACHINA ROBINSON: Obviously I cannot speak on behalf of the committee or U.S.A. Basketball, but I also do not know for sure that that is the reason why they did not attend those camps.\", \"from\": 26184, \"to\": 26368, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"LACHINA ROBINSON\", \"from\": 26184, \"to\": 26200}, {\"ngram\": \"behalf\", \"from\": 26230, \"to\": 26236}, {\"ngram\": \"the committee\", \"from\": 26240, \"to\": 26253}, {\"ngram\": \"U.S.A. Basketball\", \"from\": 26257, \"to\": 26274}, {\"ngram\": \"the reason\", \"from\": 26321, \"to\": 26331}, {\"ngram\": \"those camps\", \"from\": 26356, \"to\": 26367}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I know there is been a lot of speculation, but I have not heard anything specifically from U.S.A. or from Caitlin or Angel as to the scheduling of that.\", \"from\": 26370, \"to\": 26522, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 26391, \"to\": 26396}, {\"ngram\": \"speculation\", \"from\": 26400, \"to\": 26411}, {\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 26434, \"to\": 26442}, {\"ngram\": \"U.S.A.\", \"from\": 26461, \"to\": 26467}, {\"ngram\": \"Caitlin\", \"from\": 26476, \"to\": 26483}, {\"ngram\": \"Angel\", \"from\": 26487, \"to\": 26492}, {\"ngram\": \"the scheduling\", \"from\": 26499, \"to\": 26513}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It would be great to have all talent available that is eligible for those tryouts and for those camps.\", \"from\": 26523, \"to\": 26625, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"all talent\", \"from\": 26549, \"to\": 26559}, {\"ngram\": \"those tryouts\", \"from\": 26591, \"to\": 26604}, {\"ngram\": \"those camps\", \"from\": 26613, \"to\": 26624}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Obviously when it comes to the college basketball season there are games scheduled and mandatory things that are already set in place.\", \"from\": 26626, \"to\": 26760, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the college basketball season\", \"from\": 26653, \"to\": 26682}, {\"ngram\": \"games\", \"from\": 26693, \"to\": 26698}, {\"ngram\": \"mandatory things\", \"from\": 26713, \"to\": 26729}, {\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 26754, \"to\": 26759}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I know that it is already very tough to pull together those camps for U.S.A. because so many of their players are playing internationally and have other obligations throughout the year, and I think that's what makes this pool very special is they all try their best and put various commitments aside to be there if they can.\", \"from\": 26762, \"to\": 27086, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"those camps\", \"from\": 26816, \"to\": 26827}, {\"ngram\": \"U.S.A.\", \"from\": 26832, \"to\": 26838}, {\"ngram\": \"their players\", \"from\": 26858, \"to\": 26871}, {\"ngram\": \"other obligations\", \"from\": 26909, \"to\": 26926}, {\"ngram\": \"the year\", \"from\": 26938, \"to\": 26946}, {\"ngram\": \"this pool\", \"from\": 26978, \"to\": 26987}, {\"ngram\": \"various commitments\", \"from\": 27036, \"to\": 27055}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But, yeah, of course, you want everyone to have a fair shot.\", \"from\": 27088, \"to\": 27148, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"course\", \"from\": 27102, \"to\": 27108}, {\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 27119, \"to\": 27127}, {\"ngram\": \"a fair shot\", \"from\": 27136, \"to\": 27147}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So we are talking about something as simple as scheduling, absolutely.\", \"from\": 27149, \"to\": 27219, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 27173, \"to\": 27182}, {\"ngram\": \"scheduling\", \"from\": 27196, \"to\": 27206}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hopefully it will be something that they take into consideration moving forward.\", \"from\": 27220, \"to\": 27300, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 27241, \"to\": 27250}, {\"ngram\": \"consideration\", \"from\": 27271, \"to\": 27284}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Q. Noah, following up on the question you just got.\", \"from\": 27302, \"to\": 27353, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 27302, \"end\": 27304, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Quaternary\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Q.\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Quaternary\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Quaternary\"}, {\"begin\": 27305, \"end\": 27309, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah\", \"score\": 0.9619188453604581, \"rank\": 0.013738259540172793, \"text\": \"Noah\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q43115\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the question\", \"from\": 27327, \"to\": 27339}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This has been an incredible year because you did not only what you talked about with the French Open and the Olympics but also Big Ten football and basketball.\", \"from\": 27354, \"to\": 27513, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an incredible year\", \"from\": 27368, \"to\": 27386}, {\"ngram\": \"the French Open\", \"from\": 27439, \"to\": 27454}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 27459, \"to\": 27471}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Nickelodeon Super Bowl with Nate Burleson.\", \"from\": 27514, \"to\": 27560, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 27518, \"end\": 27529, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nickelodeon\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.71787064422547e-17, \"text\": \"Nickelodeon\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nickelodeon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nickelodeon\"}, {\"begin\": 27530, \"end\": 27540, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Super_Bowl\", \"score\": 0.9989088760297472, \"rank\": 0.0003027680862250915, \"text\": \"Super Bowl\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Super_Bowl\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Super_Bowl\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Nate Burleson\", \"from\": 27546, \"to\": 27559}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Basketball with Sara Kustok on YES.\", \"from\": 27561, \"to\": 27596, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Basketball\", \"from\": 27561, \"to\": 27571}, {\"ngram\": \"Sara Kustok\", \"from\": 27577, \"to\": 27588}, {\"ngram\": \"YES\", \"from\": 27592, \"to\": 27595}]}, {\"sentence\": \"What has it been like for you to work with so many different commentators, including the fact with the situation of the Olympics you are working with two commentators and working with learning the whole international basketball platform, what's it been like -- what do you think about yourself in terms of how you get the best out of not only yourself but also the people alongside you with commentators?\", \"from\": 27597, \"to\": 28001, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"so many different commentators\", \"from\": 27640, \"to\": 27670}, {\"ngram\": \"the fact\", \"from\": 27682, \"to\": 27690}, {\"ngram\": \"the situation\", \"from\": 27696, \"to\": 27709}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 27713, \"to\": 27725}, {\"ngram\": \"two commentators\", \"from\": 27747, \"to\": 27763}, {\"ngram\": \"the whole international basketball platform\", \"from\": 27790, \"to\": 27833}, {\"ngram\": \"terms\", \"from\": 27894, \"to\": 27899}, {\"ngram\": \"the people\", \"from\": 27958, \"to\": 27968}, {\"ngram\": \"commentators\", \"from\": 27988, \"to\": 28000}]}, {\"sentence\": \"NOAH EAGLE: I think that I was really fortunate in a lot of ways to grow up around this with my father and to see how he did it.\", \"from\": 28003, \"to\": 28131, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"NOAH EAGLE\", \"from\": 28003, \"to\": 28013}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 28054, \"to\": 28059}, {\"ngram\": \"ways\", \"from\": 28063, \"to\": 28067}, {\"ngram\": \"my father\", \"from\": 28096, \"to\": 28105}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But if I just look at all the skill sets he possessed as a broadcaster, the one that's probably the most underrated and might be the number one of making a great broadcaster is how you work with who you work with.\", \"from\": 28132, \"to\": 28345, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"all the skill sets\", \"from\": 28154, \"to\": 28172}, {\"ngram\": \"a broadcaster\", \"from\": 28189, \"to\": 28202}, {\"ngram\": \"the one\", \"from\": 28204, \"to\": 28211}, {\"ngram\": \"the number\", \"from\": 28261, \"to\": 28271}, {\"ngram\": \"a great broadcaster\", \"from\": 28286, \"to\": 28305}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And that's not just the partners that you have on the air, exactly what you mentioned, it's producer, director, graphics coordinator, A-2, cameramen, whatever it might be, statisticians.\", \"from\": 28346, \"to\": 28532, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"just the partners\", \"from\": 28361, \"to\": 28378}, {\"ngram\": \"the air\", \"from\": 28396, \"to\": 28403}, {\"ngram\": \"exactly what\", \"from\": 28405, \"to\": 28417}, {\"ngram\": \"producer\", \"from\": 28438, \"to\": 28446}, {\"ngram\": \"director\", \"from\": 28448, \"to\": 28456}, {\"ngram\": \"graphics coordinator\", \"from\": 28458, \"to\": 28478}, {\"ngram\": \"A-2\", \"from\": 28480, \"to\": 28483}, {\"ngram\": \"cameramen\", \"from\": 28485, \"to\": 28494}, {\"ngram\": \"whatever\", \"from\": 28496, \"to\": 28504}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You need to have that team atmosphere.\", \"from\": 28533, \"to\": 28571, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that team atmosphere\", \"from\": 28550, \"to\": 28570}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I watched him do it.\", \"from\": 28573, \"to\": 28593, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I would go with him -- everyone always thinks my dad sat me down one day and said this is how you become a broadcaster, right, you do this, this, and this and that's it.\", \"from\": 28594, \"to\": 28763, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 28617, \"to\": 28625}, {\"ngram\": \"my dad\", \"from\": 28640, \"to\": 28646}, {\"ngram\": \"a broadcaster\", \"from\": 28699, \"to\": 28712}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That could not be further from the truth.\", \"from\": 28764, \"to\": 28805, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the truth\", \"from\": 28795, \"to\": 28804}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I would go with him at a very young age and just watch and observe.\", \"from\": 28806, \"to\": 28873, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a very young age\", \"from\": 28829, \"to\": 28845}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I would see as he would connect with somebody that I would have never even recognized whether it was a security guy at MetLife Stadium or, quite literally, the producer of his show.\", \"from\": 28875, \"to\": 29056, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"somebody\", \"from\": 28912, \"to\": 28920}, {\"ngram\": \"a security guy\", \"from\": 28976, \"to\": 28990}, {\"ngram\": \"MetLife Stadium\", \"from\": 28994, \"to\": 29009}, {\"ngram\": \"quite literally, the producer\", \"from\": 29014, \"to\": 29043}, {\"ngram\": \"his show\", \"from\": 29047, \"to\": 29055}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was as if it was the same.\", \"from\": 29057, \"to\": 29086, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I looked at that and I said, okay, maybe that's the secret sauce I should be using myself.\", \"from\": 29088, \"to\": 29178, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the secret sauce\", \"from\": 29136, \"to\": 29152}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So I have taken that with me.\", \"from\": 29179, \"to\": 29208, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And I think it's all about connecting at an actual personal level.\", \"from\": 29209, \"to\": 29275, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an actual personal level\", \"from\": 29250, \"to\": 29274}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Dwyane talked about it a little bit but getting to know the people you are working with and legitimately taking a genuine interest in those people is paramount.\", \"from\": 29277, \"to\": 29437, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Dwyane\", \"from\": 29277, \"to\": 29283}, {\"ngram\": \"the people\", \"from\": 29333, \"to\": 29343}, {\"ngram\": \"a genuine interest\", \"from\": 29389, \"to\": 29407}, {\"ngram\": \"those people\", \"from\": 29411, \"to\": 29423}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I will say both Dwyane and LaChina are two of the most considerate analysts I have ever had because Dwyane literally brushes his teeth before every game we do and LaChina always goes with Tic Tacs.\", \"from\": 29439, \"to\": 29636, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 29627, \"end\": 29635, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tic_Tac\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tic Tacs\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tic_Tac\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tic_Tac\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"both Dwyane\", \"from\": 29450, \"to\": 29461}, {\"ngram\": \"LaChina\", \"from\": 29466, \"to\": 29473}, {\"ngram\": \"the most considerate analysts\", \"from\": 29485, \"to\": 29514}, {\"ngram\": \"Dwyane\", \"from\": 29539, \"to\": 29545}, {\"ngram\": \"his teeth\", \"from\": 29564, \"to\": 29573}, {\"ngram\": \"every game\", \"from\": 29581, \"to\": 29591}, {\"ngram\": \"LaChina\", \"from\": 29602, \"to\": 29609}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So I have got two analysts that have impeccable breath.\", \"from\": 29637, \"to\": 29692, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"two analysts\", \"from\": 29651, \"to\": 29663}, {\"ngram\": \"impeccable breath\", \"from\": 29674, \"to\": 29691}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That is massive.\", \"from\": 29693, \"to\": 29709, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That's a huge deal right off the bat.\", \"from\": 29710, \"to\": 29747, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a huge deal\", \"from\": 29717, \"to\": 29728}, {\"ngram\": \"the bat\", \"from\": 29739, \"to\": 29746}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(Laughter) Creates awesome synergy and just chemistry.\", \"from\": 29748, \"to\": 29802, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"(Laughter\", \"from\": 29748, \"to\": 29757}, {\"ngram\": \"awesome synergy\", \"from\": 29767, \"to\": 29782}, {\"ngram\": \"just chemistry\", \"from\": 29787, \"to\": 29801}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But I think when you get to know the people you are working with, you take a genuine interest in them and you actually remember the minute details they tell you.\", \"from\": 29804, \"to\": 29965, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the people\", \"from\": 29837, \"to\": 29847}, {\"ngram\": \"a genuine interest\", \"from\": 29879, \"to\": 29897}, {\"ngram\": \"the minute details\", \"from\": 29932, \"to\": 29950}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's not going in one ear and out the other.\", \"from\": 29966, \"to\": 30010, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"one ear\", \"from\": 29984, \"to\": 29991}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am trying to pay attention and actually care about what they have to say to me.\", \"from\": 30012, \"to\": 30093, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"attention\", \"from\": 30031, \"to\": 30040}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I just think that little things like that and being a decent human being go a long, long way when you are then building it on the actual camera time.\", \"from\": 30094, \"to\": 30243, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"little things\", \"from\": 30112, \"to\": 30125}, {\"ngram\": \"a decent human being\", \"from\": 30146, \"to\": 30166}, {\"ngram\": \"the actual camera time\", \"from\": 30220, \"to\": 30242}]}, {\"sentence\": \"- NBC OLYMPICS - A Division ofNBCUniversal.\", \"from\": 30245, \"to\": 30289, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 30263, \"end\": 30273, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scottish_Football_League\", \"score\": 0.9999930086210014, \"rank\": 6.3513803711628725e-06, \"text\": \"A Division\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scottish_Football_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scottish_Football_League\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"DISCLAIMER: This site and the products offered are for entertainment purposes only, and there is no gambling offered on this site.\", \"from\": 30291, \"to\": 30421, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"DISCLAIMER\", \"from\": 30291, \"to\": 30301}, {\"ngram\": \"This site\", \"from\": 30303, \"to\": 30312}, {\"ngram\": \"the products\", \"from\": 30317, \"to\": 30329}, {\"ngram\": \"entertainment purposes\", \"from\": 30346, \"to\": 30368}, {\"ngram\": \"no gambling\", \"from\": 30388, \"to\": 30399}, {\"ngram\": \"this site\", \"from\": 30411, \"to\": 30420}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This service is intended for adult audiences.\", \"from\": 30422, \"to\": 30467, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This service\", \"from\": 30422, \"to\": 30434}, {\"ngram\": \"adult audiences\", \"from\": 30451, \"to\": 30466}]}, {\"sentence\": \"No guarantees are made for any specific outcome.\", \"from\": 30468, \"to\": 30516, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"No guarantees\", \"from\": 30468, \"to\": 30481}, {\"ngram\": \"any specific outcome\", \"from\": 30495, \"to\": 30515}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If you or someone you know has a gambling problem, please call 1-800-GAMBLER.\", \"from\": 30517, \"to\": 30594, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"someone\", \"from\": 30527, \"to\": 30534}, {\"ngram\": \"a gambling problem\", \"from\": 30548, \"to\": 30566}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u24b8 2024 NBC Universal\", \"from\": 30596, \"to\": 30616, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u24b8 2024 NBC Universal\", \"from\": 30596, \"to\": 30616}]}]}"